---
title: Bavette Steak & Sherry Shallot Sauce with Garlic Parmesan Potato Clusters & Mixed Greens
description: People who cook fancier weeknight dinners are more likely to receive a compliment from a stranger, meet their celebrity crush, and/or win the lottery. Ok, we made most of that up, but they are guaranteed to be rewarded a delicious, steakhouse-quality meal without leaving the comforts of their kitchen. Case in point: these seared bavette steaks drizzled in a deluxe, sherry vinegar-spiked pan sauce with crispy, cheesy potatoes and a tangy mixed greens salad.
